        <p>50% of Americans are magnesium deficient, and deficiency is directly linked to increased anxiety. Magnesium glycinate enhances GABA receptor activity while the glycine component provides independent anxiolytic effects. Addresses the mineral root cause of anxiety in deficient individuals.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

